{"tid":2200234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參加反政府示威遭酷刑逼供 伊朗無視國際要求赦免呼籲 摔角冠軍被秘密處決","createTime":"2020-09-12T19:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T04:06:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4812cbcb2abf1472729945be81cc0a4a36bc0b92","tid":2200234,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T19:08:55.000Z","msg":"伊朗無視國際要求赦免的呼籲，處決一名涉嫌謀殺的摔跤手。<br />\n<br />\n27歲的阿夫卡里被指在2018年的反政府示威中，殺死一名自來水公司的保安員，被裁定謀殺罪成，判處死刑，當地星期六早上被處決。<br />\n<br />\n家人曾經表示，阿夫卡里是在酷刑下被迫認罪，代表律師亦認為，無證據證明他的當事人有罪，又說當局拒絕在行刑前，讓家人探望阿夫卡里。<br />\n<br />\n阿夫卡里的案件引發國際關注，國際奧委會主席巴赫形容，阿夫卡里被處決是非常不幸及悲傷的消息。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普曾經為阿夫卡里求情，形容對方唯一的行為就是在街上參與反政府示威。代表全球85000名運動員的世界運動員協會早前說，如果伊朗堅持行刑，就應該將伊朗逐出世界體育之中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549305-20200913.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549305-20200913.htm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513S%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=149ff8d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549305-20200913.htm&h=c4911db1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549305-20200913.htm</a>"},{"pid":"355df864cbcea7403ba2bbffa0f22373cab46dbf","tid":2200234,"uid":239392,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T19:22:57.000Z","msg":"共匪仲同佢走咁埋，死得"},{"pid":"fd9573422fec9a31bed4c043bb5463d67e612ab6","tid":2200234,"uid":278533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"355df864cbcea7403ba2bbffa0f22373cab46dbf","tid":2200234,"uid":239392,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T19:22:57.000Z","msg":"共匪仲同佢走咁埋，死得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T19:30:42.000Z","msg":"死乜尻 二個半斤八兩極權閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62843468b5f82bb3474cb34edaef7ddf9a85d29","tid":2200234,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fd9573422fec9